branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series VCH41/42 is a 3 port pilot operated solenoid valve for high pressure application.&#xa0;Designed for use with air or inert gas, the VCH valve can operate up to a maximum pressure of 5.0 MPa. With reduction in the overall volume of the pilot chamber, the VCH&apos;s responsiveness can now be measured in just milliseconds. Non-collision armature construction, rubber buffers and a urethane diaphragm give the VCH series an expected service life of 10 million cycles.
&lt;/p&gt;

